value.string: Super Luxury Off The Grid!!! Custom 2,264 sqft home on 5 manicured North Shore acres! This estate is in perfect condition. Meticulous maintenance standards. Electric power is generated on property; full communications center gourmet chef's kitchen. Private owners suite, outstanding inventory and landscaping. So near yet so far removed. Prime horse country! Experience fine living.

This Wailuku Heights home has gorgeous views of Haleakala and the central Valley, including the north and south shores from almost every room in the house. These views are not likely to ever be obstructed as the home is on the mauka side of the street across from a public park. Enjoy the cool breezes and spetacular views from the covered porches of this very comfortable home. Downstairs has a kitchenette and a two car garage. This is one of those homes that is the very essence comfort and convenience with a view. Tenant occupied please allow 48 hour notice to show. Tenants on one year lease
